data.description: Beautifully maintained single-story 4 bedroom/2 bath home nestled in the sought-after Champion Springs community! The designer-like kitchen and bathrooms offer modern elegance. Enjoy the inviting open floor plan accented by the high ceilings, with tile flooring in main areas. The chef's kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a convenient island with extra counter space, complete with a stylish wine rack above the refrigerator. The spacious living room features a striking stone wall accent with ambient lighting and an electric light-changing fireplace. With the option to use heat or cool air, the fireplace is perfect for any evening! Retreat to the luxurious Primary Suite, which boasts ample space and a huge walk-in closet with built-in storage cut-outs. The primary bath welcomes you with granite countertops, a double sink vanity offering plenty of storage, and a rejuvenating standing shower equipped with an oversized rain shower head (color changing). Additional bedrooms offer generous proportions and ample closet space, with the 4th bedroom versatile for use as an office or media room. Outside, the expansive backyard features a covered patio, ideal for enjoying tranquil evenings or hosting lively BBQs with friends and family. Conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping, and entertainment, with the added bonuses of a new roof installed in July 2020 and a new AC unit in November 2019. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and location/convenience for modern living. Book your showing today!
